Body (HTML):

Title: AkcesMed Aurora Stroller
Body (HTML):
• Aurora® is an advanced special needs stroller that combines a new generation design with a modern look. The biggest advantage of the Aurora® stroller is its convenient multifunctional reversible seat. A tilt-in-space function allows for smooth adjustment of the inclination angle of the entire seat. The adjustable cushions and side supports provide excellent lateral stabilization. In addition, there is the possibility of changing the height of the headrest, the angle of the backrest and the footrest.
    • SPECIFICATION
  • Seat width (with narrowing pad)[cm]: 18
  • Seat width (without narrowing pad)[cm]: 27
  • Seat depth[cm]: 30
  • Maximum user weight[kg]: 40

Title: AkcesMed Cat1 Standing Frame
Body (HTML):
• Stander CAT I™ was created with a view to help children in adoption of the upright position. The upright standing contributes to the acquisition by children a new experience from the nearest environment and stimulates their psycho-physical development. There are many advantages during use of the CAT I™.

Title: AkcesMed Cat II Invento
Body (HTML):
• Stander CAT II Invento™ enables individual approach to the needs of a child and his family. Correct configuration of this device makes it possible to stand in either prone or supine position depending on the locomotor system dysfunction and on medical / therapeutic indications. Infinitely adjustable tilt angle (from 0° to 90°) allows you to change the position from lying down to standing.
